item.title: What I Use
item.description: For the few times I have to tell people in detail the software and hardware I use on a day to day basis to do my job, here’s a post to list them. My setup changes from time to time but I’ll try to keep this up to date. My dotfiles can be found on This Repo - they work for me, read carefully before installing for yourself. Hardware HP 24” Monitor: HP24y IPS Display MacBook Pro 13” (2017) 2.
